snippet.description:

Learn more about this incredible SNES homebrew at Nintendo Life:

https://www.nintendolife.com/news/2019/11/feature_the_story_behind_new_super_mario_land_the_homebrew_marvel_intended_as_a_christmas_gift


Thank you for visiting Shiryu @ YouTube! Hope you find me video gaming memories a useful resource and/or enjoy my music producing hobby. It has always been my belief that both music and video games are universal languages, meaning they can be enjoyed by everyone, everywhere around the globe. Your support and feedback is greatly appreciated and I will do my best to reply to every comment on my videos. - Shiryu
